knowledgeTasks.name: Travel Assistant
knowledgeTasks.description: This is used to make ontology

answer.text:
An eticket (electronic ticket) is a paperless
electronic document with a unique
confirmation number that neatly replaces the
hassles of a paper ticket. When you purchase
an eticket, we email it to you after the
booking is complete. Simply print it out and
bring it with you  along with a valid photo ID
 to the airline counter when checking in for
your flight.

faqs.question: How do I get my e-ticket details
faqs.label: How do I get my e-ticket details

answer.text:
Well send your eticket details to the email
address you gave us when you made your
reservation.

faqs.question: How do I know my reservation was booked
faqs.label: How do I know my reservation was booked

answer.text:
Well send you an SMS and an email to

confirm your flight booking.

the cancellation charges depend on the
airline, sector, class of booking, and time of
cancellation.

faqs.question: How do I print my ticket
faqs.label: How do I print my ticket

answer.text:
Enter your mobile number and youll be able
to see your eticket. Print it or email it.

faqs.question:
I need to cancel my flight, whats the latest I
can do this by
faqs.label:
I need to cancel my flight, whats the latest I
can do this by

answer.text:
you can cancel your flight no later than 3
hours before the time of departure.
